MAIN_MESSAGE: There is a power cut in the L31, L32 and L39 postcode areas of Liverpool and Ormskirk. Repairs are taking longer than expected because of further network investigations required and our team are now working to get your power back on as quickly and as safely as possible in stages by 10.00PM. We will update this message if this information changes. We apologise for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience. This message was updated at 7.18PM on 17th November 2020.
